        private void saveSession(java.lang.String directory,

               java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String[]> nameImgGen)

        directory - absolute path to the directory where all files will be saved
        nameSpectra - an arrayList of names of the saved Spectras
        nameImgGen - an arrayList of names of the saved ImageGenerateds
